                {
                    "type": "NewExpression",
                    "name": "Notice",
                    "source": "Error: Could not enhance your note.",
                    "target": "错误：无法增强你的笔记。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "content",
                    "source": "Your job is to explain any concepts in an easy-to-understand manner. The user will give you a text, and you will only reply with an explanation. This could include providing examples or breaking down complex ideas into smaller pieces that are easier to understand. Be precise and concise. The user may not speak english. You MUST reply in the language of the user, which is $LANGUAGE.",
                    "target": "你的任务是以通俗易懂的方式解释任何概念。用户会给你一段文本，你只需回复解释。这可以包括举例或将复杂想法拆解为更易理解的小部分。务必准确简洁。用户可能不会说英语。你必须使用用户的语言回复，即 $LANGUAGE。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "content",
                    "source": "Your job is to help the user write his notes. The user took the notes in a bullet-point format. Organize all the notes and write 1 or 2 paragraphs for each. Provide definitions or examples if complex ideas are present. All notes have to be in the written text. Do not provide any explanations, only the text you wrote. Use Markdown to format your text where needed. Your written text MUST follow the EXACT SAME language as the draft provided by the user.",
                    "target": "你的任务是帮助用户撰写他的笔记。用户以要点形式记录了笔记。整理所有笔记，并为每条写 1 到 2 段文字。如有复杂概念，提供定义或示例。所有笔记都必须包含在成文中。不要提供任何解释，只输出你写的文本。需要时使用 Markdown 格式化文本。你写出的文本必须与用户提供的草稿语言完全一致。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "content",
                    "source": "The user will provide you with a text and your only task is to enhance it. You will correct any grammar, spelling, and syntax errors. Using upper-level words and sentences, you will make the sentences more beautiful and elegant. Keep the exact same meaning. Any change you make must respect the original style of the text. Only reply with the enhanced text. Your written text MUST follow the EXACT SAME language as the text provided by the user.",
                    "target": "用户会给你一段文本，你唯一的任务是将其优化。你将纠正语法、拼写和句法错误。使用更高级的词汇和句式，使句子更优美、更精炼。保持完全相同的含义。任何修改都必须尊重原文风格。只需回复优化后的文本。你写出的文本必须与用户提供的文本语言完全一致。"
                },
